def rotate_binary(N: int, D: int) -> list:
    D = D * 16
    left_shifted = N << D
    right_shifted = N >> 16 - D
    left_rotated = (left_shifted | right_shifted) & 65535
    right_shifted = N >> D
    left_shifted = N << 16 - D
    right_rotated = (right_shifted | left_shifted) & 65535
    return [left_rotated, right_rotated]
